<h2>So What?</h2>

<p>Many will ask why or what&#8217;s the big deal. If you&#8217;ve built add-ons in ExpressionEngine, then you probably already see why this is a big deal. Add-ons bring a lot of power to ExpressionEngine sites, and we hope that with this new paradigm, the barrier to add-on development will begin to fall. Anyone should be able to create a template tag or a fieldtype, and it shouldn&#8217;t take them long to do so. Who thought we could have a working custom fieldtype in under 1 minute? This is how ExpressionEngine add-on development should be.</p>
